channel.title: [317] TyL3rs Pk FIRST RELEASE!~[317]
channel.description:
First off, CREDITS! *SkillerDream for base -In Command prompt (runserver) *Silabsoft TuTs (helped alottt) *Me- Editting =D
Been editing on and off for awhile and decided to release becuase im moving on to 508's. This is only my first source, I will probably be releasing a 508 sometime, So enjoy it~!
[b]Features[/b] [code]* New Home - With portals to south * Armadyl Minigame - Full armadyl at end * Max level is 110. * More realistic Strength bonuses * Max DDs spec 45/45 - dbow 50/50 * Barrows * Pkarena - Includes 2 areas; Left side 1V1 - Cannot team :) ; Right Side FunPk -Lose Nothing,No freezing * Skill Area - Added Fishing spots * More realistic Vengeance * Noclip = Jailed * Added Emote Tabs * Created Bounty Area - I thought it was pretty neat * Added Anti - SYI and Null - Works perfectly :P * New shop area - added Void * TeamPk Area * Edge Pk :) * ChurchPk + more, check it out yourself XD[/code]
[b]Commands[/b]
[code][b]Normal[/b] *::char *::modinfo *::afk *::back *::shout *::starter *::suggest
[b]Mod[/b] *Staff Area Access *::banuser *::kick *::mute *::xteleto
[b]Admin[/b] *::Master *::xteletome *::god *::pickup *::xrichie *::unban *::evil *::good *::pimp *::unjail (noclippers) And More I Cannot Think Of (look in client.java for more)
[b]Owner[/b] *::ipban *::emote *::hail *::hump *::dp1-8 (drop party) *::givemod *::giveadmin *::giveowner (Only Actual owner; change my name(tyl3r) to yours) + More I can't Think Of.[/code]
And the pictures
Funpk Side of PkArena [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/100.jpg[/img]
Home Area [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/101.jpg[/img]
Basic Shops [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/102.jpg[/img]
TeamPk Area [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/103.jpg[/img]
Barrows [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/104.jpg[/img]
Bounty Area [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/105.jpg[/img]
ChurchPk Area [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/106.jpg[/img]
Anti-SYI & Null [img]http://i464.photobucket.com/albums/rr3/Mr_Ferri/107.jpg[/img]
THERES MORE THAN THAT- DOWNLAOD TO SEE! :P
Well Theres my first server I have made. Please DONT FLAME, it's only my first server :)
LINKS!
[url=http://uppit.com/YDSEG1]http://uppit.com/YDSEG1[/url] [url=http://uppit.com/YDSEG1]http://uppit.com/YDSEG1[/url] [url=http://uppit.com/YDSEG1]http://uppit.com/YDSEG1[/url] [url=http://uppit.com/YDSEG1]http://uppit.com/YDSEG1[/url] [url=http://uppit.com/YDSEG1]http://uppit.com/YDSEG1[/url]

THANKS!
